node.text: The fact that he places his feet on the opposite seats just makes me feel like WTH ? PEOPLE SIT ON THOSE SEATS TOO DAMN IT

You see an uncle with his feet on the seat, I see an old man who might be tired after many years of Nation building; so the millenial generation can snap pictures in AC bus under a favorable economy and safe environment. Try to be more tolerant towards those who have made Singapore the paradise it is.
